        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "The ministers looked at each other with surprise.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "The others, a little uneasy at the turn things had taken, went back to Paris together.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "After dinner, he got into his carriage, and went straight to the Louvre.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000003_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000003_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "There he received much company, and took a degree of pleasure in remarking the hesitation of each, and the curiosity of all.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000003_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000003_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "Towards evening he ordered the doors of the Louvre to be closed, with the exception of only one, which opened on the quay.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000003_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000003_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "He placed on duty at this point two hundred Swiss, who did not speak a word of French, with orders to admit all who carried packages, but no others; and by no means to allow any one to go out.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000003_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000003_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "Soon after, somebody scratched with his nail at the door of the cabinet.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "This review completed, Louis returned to his apartments, followed by Colbert, who had not apparently warmed with one ray of personal satisfaction.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Monsieur,\" said the king, \"what do you wish that I should give you, as a recompense for this devotedness and probity?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Absolutely nothing, sire.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"How! nothing?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "Not even an opportunity of serving me?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"If your majesty were not to furnish me with that opportunity, I should not the less serve you.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "It is impossible for me not to be the best servant of the king.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"But there is already a superintendent, sire.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
