        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"I know that.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Sire, the superintendent of the finances is the most powerful man in the kingdom.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Ah!\" cried Louis, coloring, \"do you think so?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"He will crush me in a week, sire.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "An intendant under a superintendent,--that is inferiority.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"You want support-you do not reckon upon me?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Then I shall be of no use to your majesty?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"You are already, since you fear to compromise yourself in serving me.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"I only fear to be placed so that I cannot serve your majesty.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"What do you wish, then?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"I wish your majesty to allow me assistance in the labors of the office of intendant.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"That post would lose its value.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"It would gain in security.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Choose your colleagues.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"To morrow the ordonnance shall appear.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Sire, I thank you.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Is that all you ask?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"No, sire, one thing more.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Allow me to compose a chamber of justice.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"What would this chamber of justice do?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Try the farmers general and contractors, who, during ten years, have been robbing the state.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"On the contrary, sire, you had better, in order not to have to end with them.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "The king made no reply.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"I will reflect upon it, monsieur.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"It will be too late when reflection may be made.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Why?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Because you have to deal with people stronger than ourselves, if they are warned.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"I will, sire.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Is that all?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"No, sire; there is still another important affair.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000048_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000048_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Well-I do not know-the customary ones.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000049_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000049_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Sire, I desire that this office be invested with the right of reading the correspondence with England.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000050_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000050_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Impossible, monsieur, for that correspondence is kept from the council; monsieur le cardinal himself carried it on.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000051_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000051_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"I thought your majesty had this morning declared that there should no longer be a council?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000052_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000052_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Yes, I said so.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000053_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000053_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Let your majesty then have the goodness to read all the letters yourself, particularly those from England; I hold strongly to this article.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Monsieur, you shall have that correspondence, and render me an account of it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000055_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000055_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"Now, sire, what shall I do with respect to the finances?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000057_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000057_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "The following is what the English prince wrote to his royal brother:--",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000058_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000058_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "The cardinal is given over by his physician.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000058_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000058_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "It is gratifying to me to acknowledge the fraternal friendship you have evinced towards me, and to call you, more justly than ever, my brother.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000058_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000058_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "That is wrong.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000058_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000058_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "We shall never be at war against each other.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000058_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000058_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "That measure does not make me uneasy, it makes me sad.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000058_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000058_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "You are spending useless millions; tell your ministers so; and rest assured that I am well informed; render me the same service, my brother, if occasion offers.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000059_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000059_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "Let him be called back!\" exclaimed he.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000060_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000060_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "The valet was about to execute the order, when the king stopped him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000061_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000061_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "\"No,\" said he, \"no; I see the whole scheme of that man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6368_39664_000061_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6368/39664/6368_39664_000061_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6368",
        "content": "Oh! but I cannot place all my dependence upon that man; he has a good head, but I must have an arm!\" Louis, all at once, uttered a joyful cry.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
